(1215, 'Le petit Nicolas', '2007-03-01', 3, 1, 239, 447, 4, 3, 'https://libris.to/media/jacket/04406671_le-petit-nicolas.jpg', NULL, 'Told from the perspective of a young French boy, this collection of charming stories--presented in French--isn\'t just for young readers. It doubles as an entertaining primer for anyone who is studying the French language.'),
